{"tid":2074354,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"千與千尋－ 千尋 同 白龍 之後會再相遇，有冇人覺得？","createTime":"2020-06-22T04:59:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T13:35:01.000Z","uid":225542,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9b73b8eb34a39a88cd1b3157d7a37ebc672cb274","tid":2074354,"uid":225542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T04:59:15.000Z","msg":"睇方間解讀話 白龍最後個句 其實暗示佢忘記依個世界 即係千出翻去後 佢地都唔會再見<br />\n<br />\n但我覺得作者角度出發 其實冇依個意思 只係將佢地之後係現實世界相遇嘅過程同遭遇留白 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解啲人會上綱上線到白龍句咁普通嘅約定 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db1b4bc1df2569375f90e3dd8e8a44310b2a97d","tid":2074354,"uid":225422,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T05:42:52.000Z","msg":"轉生咗做塔始亮 應該無咩可能再見"},{"pid":"2ad63e67a6647c3fa17913744fc82673249a06ba","tid":2074354,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T05:47:39.000Z","msg":"喺果個世界入面既然靈魂可以獨立存在 咁再次遇見又有幾難"},{"pid":"9572dd834f1ae02d4af8613f88af07b51c1fab93","tid":2074354,"uid":51753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4db1b4bc1df2569375f90e3dd8e8a44310b2a97d","tid":2074354,"uid":225422,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T05:42:52.000Z","msg":"轉生咗做塔始亮 應該無咩可能再見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T05:48:43.000Z","msg":"伊紮古 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一級方程式果個"},{"pid":"674e85933322467b3109c85d88a7b50eafa61108","tid":2074354,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T06:26:06.000Z","msg":"腦補 一定會再見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a866a5c4dd5f674b9f9cd60b6cdef5bf9b2d057","tid":2074354,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:59:55.000Z","msg":"果個婆婆會報仇<br />\n好難"},{"pid":"18f420b0b5f8e3d0925e5c52223e94614574a341","tid":2074354,"uid":50891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T13:35:01.000Z","msg":"我